Project Nebula addresses the critical challenge of training machine learning models on decentralized sensitive data while maintaining GDPR/CCPA compliance. Unlike traditional centralized approaches, our framework implements a hybrid federated learning architecture that supports both cross-silo and cross-device scenarios.
